Comment: 1,0:02:18.87,0:02:20.87,JP-Main-Down,,0,0,0,,正文
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.87,0:02:22.48,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,何これー
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.48,0:02:24.09,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留ちゃん大丈夫
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.09,0:02:27.73,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,これきっとさっきのちっちゃいのにやられたんだよ　きっと
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.73,0:02:28.83,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,生きてる
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.83,0:02:30.62,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,全然　とれない
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.62,0:02:31.83,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留ちゃんは
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.00,0:02:36.91,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,駄目
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.91,0:02:39.97,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,てかものすごく撃たれたよね　ミサイルっぽいのも
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.97,0:02:42.27,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ポインじゃなくて　ミサイル　ミサイル
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.27,0:02:44.06,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,それ以外も　ミニミニソルジャーが
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.06,0:02:45.97,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,バンバン撃ってきた　痛がゆいの
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.97,0:02:47.16,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,きっとあれだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.16,0:02:49.74,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ちっちゃいから　威力もちっちゃいいんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.74,0:02:50.55,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,そうなの
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.55,0:02:51.68,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,わからん　たぶん
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.68,0:02:54.07,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,それより　これどんなきゃ
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.28,0:02:54.81,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,8,,{\an8}そうだ　そうだね
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.81,0:02:57.61,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ああ　もう
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.05,0:03:15.01,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,お前たち　一体何者だ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.30,0:03:16.89,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,まず　これとって
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.89,0:03:17.70,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,答えろ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.70,0:03:19.08,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,やだ　とったら話す
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.30,0:03:22.59,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,ならば　死ぬまでそうしているがいい
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.01,0:03:25.74,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,吾野から来たぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.57,0:03:27.82,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,吾野
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.38,0:03:30.84,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,吾野の人間も　変わっていないのか
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.84,0:03:32.91,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,も　もって
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.91,0:03:35.84,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,吾野は皆以前のままなのかと聞いている
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.84,0:03:39.18,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,私たちはまだだけど　動物ならそのうち
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.45,0:03:40.99,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,ここへは　何しに来た
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.58,0:03:43.68,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,散歩に
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.15,0:03:44.77,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,8,,{\an8}お医者さん探してんの
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.77,0:03:45.99,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なんで言うの
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.99,0:03:47.10,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,言うんじゃないの
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.10,0:03:48.88,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ちょっとずつ言おうと思ったのに
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.88,0:03:50.47,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,そんなん知らないもん
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.47,0:03:52.82,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,全部言っちゃったら　駆け引きできないじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.83,0:03:55.00,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,え　これ取ったら話すって　私言ったよ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.00,0:03:56.92,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,それでおっさんかえろとしたじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.92,0:03:59.40,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,最初から　あの態度じゃ駄目なんだって
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.40,0:04:01.02,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,おっさんムカつくんだもん
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.02,0:04:03.43,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,私だってムカつくよ　こんなおっさん
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.43,0:04:05.37,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,回せー
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.19,0:04:12.35,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,何々
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.35,0:04:14.02,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ちょちょちょっ　痛っ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.02,0:04:15.62,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ちょっとやめて
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.19,0:04:17.23,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,8,,{\an8}痛っ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.62,0:04:17.23,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,顔痛いって
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.23,0:04:17.99,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,止めろ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.19,0:04:21.90,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,うるさいんだよ　お前ら
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.90,0:04:23.88,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,今こっちが質問してんだろうが
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.88,0:04:25.44,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,勝手に喧嘩してるんじゃないよ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.44,0:04:27.29,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,喧嘩つうか　俺の悪口か
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.29,0:04:28.49,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,急にめっちゃキレて
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.49,0:04:29.49,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,キレてないわ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.49,0:04:31.13,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,誰が小娘相手にキレるか
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.13,0:04:32.32,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,隊長だぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.32,0:04:34.03,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,なんで隊長が小娘相手に
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.03,0:04:34.50,JP-Main-Down,Soldier,0,0,0,,隊長
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.50,0:04:35.94,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,わかってるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.98,0:04:39.30,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,医者を探すと言ったが　吾野にもいるだろ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.71,0:04:41.54,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ドクターって人探してる
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.33,0:04:44.82,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,なぜドクターを
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.82,0:04:46.22,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,友達に茸生えて
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.22,0:04:48.66,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,抜いちゃったから死んじゃうかもしんないの
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.66,0:04:49.73,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,茸
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.73,0:04:51.62,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,それも7Gの影響なのか
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.62,0:04:53.06,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,決まってんじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.62,0:04:54.95,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,決まってるよね
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.95,0:04:55.68,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,絶対そう
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.09,0:04:58.39,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,やはり　ボスの言っていた通りだ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.06,0:05:00.41,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,何　さっきから
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.41,0:05:01.76,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,すぐに報告に向かうぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.76,0:05:02.54,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ちょっと
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.54,0:05:04.22,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,話したんだからとってよ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.22,0:05:06.02,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,そんな約束はしていない
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.02,0:05:08.92,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,街の情報を外部の者に漏らすわけにはいかんのでな
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.92,0:05:09.81,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,なんで
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.81,0:05:12.57,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,我らが聡明なるボスがお決めになったことだ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.57,0:05:13.04,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ボス
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.44,0:05:16.68,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,ボスの命により　明日　お前たちの骨を
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.68,0:05:19.79,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,狭山市立博物館のアケボノゾウの隣に展示する
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.05,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,骨って何
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.86,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,骨にされたら死んじゃうじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.86,0:05:24.32,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,死刑じゃん　それ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.83,0:05:26.35,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,待て　これ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.35,0:05:29.56,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,放せ　この豆粒ゴミ虫
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.49,0:05:31.65,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,電流よし
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.65,0:05:32.77,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,電圧よし
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.09,0:05:33.35,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,8,,{\an8}撫子ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.35,0:05:35.88,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,アンソニー　来てなのです
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.88,0:05:37.92,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,はーい　ちょっと待ってねー
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.92,0:05:40.31,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,ぼっちさん　晶ちゃん呼んでるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.31,0:05:42.64,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,早く来るのです
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.51,0:05:43.28,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,8,,{\an8}はいはいはいはいはい　よし
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.12,0:05:45.41,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,晶ちゃん　どうした
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.41,0:05:48.76,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,玲実ちゃんと静留ちゃんはどこへ行きましたか
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.76,0:05:51.48,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,晶一人ぼっちでつまんないぷー
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.48,0:05:52.53,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,そうだね
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.53,0:05:55.09,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,きっとすぐ帰ってくるから　もうちょっと待ってよ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.09,0:05:58.59,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,絶対二人とも寄り道して　ライス食べてるんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.59,0:06:01.50,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,だから私もアンソニーと遊んでます
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.16,0:06:05.33,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,ぼっちさん　点検終わるまでお願いね
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.04,0:06:09.42,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,アンソニー　もふもふ可愛いですね
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.42,0:06:12.68,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,どんどんお顔が　キュートなってますね
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.26,0:06:15.31,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ああ　もう手痛い
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.31,0:06:17.04,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,やめんな　血出るから
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.04,0:06:18.87,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,そんな言ってる場合じゃない
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.87,0:06:20.06,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ブレースレット切れるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.95,0:06:23.05,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,私の考え聞いて
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.05,0:06:23.68,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.68,0:06:26.37,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,この街にちゃんとドクターがいるってわかった
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.37,0:06:27.08,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.08,0:06:29.02,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,あとは探すだけ　ね
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.02,0:06:29.82,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.82,0:06:31.54,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,これとる方法とかは
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.54,0:06:32.33,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,それはまだ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.33,0:06:33.03,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,そこ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.03,0:06:34.55,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,そこじゃん大事なの
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.55,0:06:36.66,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,期待した　期待して損した
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.66,0:06:39.08,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,もう　なんかないのいい方法
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.61,0:06:42.29,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ちょっとちょっと
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.29,0:06:44.16,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ちょっと待って　お姉さん待って
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.16,0:06:46.54,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,お願いこれ解いて
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.54,0:06:49.43,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,私たち危害を加えようとしてるんじゃないの
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.43,0:06:52.68,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ドクターって人に友達助けてもらいたいだけ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.41,0:06:55.14,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,あなたたちと話すと
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.14,0:06:57.84,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,ボスに骨にされて展じされてしまいます
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.84,0:06:59.58,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,だからそのボスって誰
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.58,0:07:01.59,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,話すと骨にされてしまいます
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.59,0:07:03.77,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,だったら近く来ることないじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.77,0:07:05.53,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なんか理由があったんじゃないの
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.53,0:07:09.75,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,私はここの清掃係ですから　ゴミがないかと
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.75,0:07:12.15,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,汚れていたら骨にされてしまいますし
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.15,0:07:12.98,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,じゃあじゃあ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.98,0:07:14.88,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,私らも一緒にゴミ拾ってあげる
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.88,0:07:15.92,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ちょっと
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.92,0:07:16.95,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,おしっこ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.82,0:07:19.04,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.04,0:07:20.74,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,おしっこする　ここで
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.74,0:07:22.77,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,さっきからトイレ行きたかったの
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.77,0:07:25.31,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我慢できないから　ごがておしっこする
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.05,0:07:28.70,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,公園汚れちゃうけどしょうがないよね
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.70,0:07:30.38,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,私もおしっこしちゃおう
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.38,0:07:31.63,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,めっちゃしちゃうから
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.63,0:07:32.68,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,知らない
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.68,0:07:35.20,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ほどいてくれたら絶対ボスやっつける
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.20,0:07:38.06,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留ちゃんの吾野柔術マジやばいから
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.06,0:07:39.94,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,私もなんかやばいから
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.94,0:07:42.67,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,私たち助けて骨にされるか
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.67,0:07:44.69,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,おしっこされて骨にされるか
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.69,0:07:45.87,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,どっち
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.50,0:07:48.93,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あっ　ちょっと出ちゃった
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.71,0:07:50.90,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,お姉さんありがと
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.90,0:07:52.09,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,痛たたたたたた
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.09,0:07:52.88,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あっごめん
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.88,0:07:54.09,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ボスはやっつける
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.09,0:07:55.71,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,でも先にドクターに会わせて
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.09,0:07:58.94,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,ドクターはボスに捕まってしまいました
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.94,0:08:00.45,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,えっ　嘘でしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.45,0:08:03.92,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,じゃあまずはドクターの居場所が分かる人を助けないと
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.92,0:08:05.45,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,誰もいないね
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.45,0:08:07.53,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,外出禁止令が出てますから
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.53,0:08:09.93,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,で　ドクターは何で捕まってるわけ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.38,0:08:12.35,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,じゅんをおって話しますね
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.35,0:08:17.17,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,私たちの変化は　おそらく噂の7G事件がきっかけです
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.17,0:08:21.19,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,街は膨張続けた後　反動で小さくなってしまいました
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.19,0:08:24.39,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,そんな中　住民をまとめた人がいました
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.39,0:08:25.61,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,それがドクター
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.61,0:08:27.67,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,ギャッパ・マコト・アングストルームさん
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.67,0:08:29.35,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,すご　やることも名前も
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.35,0:08:31.82,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,住民はマコト先生をリーダーとして
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.82,0:08:35.48,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,サイズ以外は問題なく生活できるレベルを維持しました
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.48,0:08:38.58,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,しかしそこに　ボスが現れたんです
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.58,0:08:41.01,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,ボスはあっという間に街を支配すると
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.01,0:08:43.41,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,リーダーだったマコト先生を捕まえ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.41,0:08:45.15,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,どこかに監禁してしまったんです
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.15,0:08:46.84,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ボスそんなめちゃ強なの
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.84,0:08:48.21,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,やがて住民は
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.21,0:08:51.00,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,ボスに従う　上等稲荷山市民と
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.00,0:08:54.81,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,自由を奪われた　下等稲荷山市民とに分かれました
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.81,0:08:58.43,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,私たち下等稲荷山市民は　全てを管理され
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.43,0:09:00.94,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,ひたすらインフラ維持のために生きています
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.94,0:09:02.87,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,インフラってボーフラの仲間
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.87,0:09:04.71,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,この街にある基地の位置と
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.71,0:09:07.41,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,ボスの趣味に使う電力を作らされているんです
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.41,0:09:08.76,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,そんなひどいじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.76,0:09:10.87,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,みんなもう諦めてる
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.87,0:09:13.52,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,でも　マコト先生が帰ってきたら
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.52,0:09:15.91,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,もう一回　立ち上がれるかもって
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.91,0:09:17.82,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,それで私らんところに
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.82,0:09:18.36,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.74,0:09:25.58,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,しずるちゃんどうしよう
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.70,0:09:44.72,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,お願い
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.72,0:09:47.05,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,マコト先生の居場所を教えた
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.05,0:09:49.35,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,元上等市民のあなたなら知ってるはず
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.15,0:09:52.07,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,あの
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.79,0:09:55.06,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,情報源は絶対ばらさない
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.06,0:09:56.18,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,えっと
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.18,0:09:58.09,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,今稲荷山公園
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.09,0:10:00.02,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,医者探してますと
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.02,0:10:02.08,JP-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,なぜ医者なんか探している
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.08,0:10:02.71,JP-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,病気か
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.71,0:10:03.42,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.42,0:10:05.93,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,晶ちゃん茸生えたって言ったじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.93,0:10:07.19,JP-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,茸聞いた
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.19,0:10:08.20,JP-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,医者なんぞ知らんぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.20,0:10:10.95,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,稲荷山にお医者さんがいるんだよね
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.95,0:10:11.91,JP-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,違う
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.91,0:10:14.85,JP-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,そうじゃな　ぼぼぼ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.22,0:10:17.45,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,撫子ちゃん困ったちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.45,0:10:18.82,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,そんな顔してた
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.82,0:10:21.76,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,実は晶も困ったちゃんなのです
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.76,0:10:24.68,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,体がずしいて動かなくなってきてね
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.92,0:10:24.68,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,8,,{\an8}晶ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.02,0:10:26.83,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,でも心配いりません
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.83,0:10:30.99,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,困ったちゃんの時は　どんな時玲実ちゃんが来てくれるのです
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.45,0:10:34.18,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,すごいお腹痛くなったんだからね
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.18,0:10:36.23,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,本当に食べちゃうと思わなかったんだもん
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.23,0:10:38.55,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,教科書なくなっちゃった
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.60,0:10:39.59,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,8,,{\an8}たくしわったせるからでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.59,0:10:41.09,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,もう晶とは絶交
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.09,0:10:42.19,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,いいもん別に
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.47,0:10:44.54,JP-Main-Down,Boy A,0,0,0,,おい　何読んでんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.29,0:10:46.55,JP-Main-Down,Boy B,0,0,0,,うわ　つまんねえ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.55,0:10:47.62,JP-Main-Down,Boy B,0,0,0,,字しかねえし
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.62,0:10:49.24,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,私は面白いもん
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.24,0:10:50.01,JP-Main-Down,Boy C,0,0,0,,えん
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.01,0:10:53.34,JP-Main-Down,Boy C,0,0,0,,お前ま西吾野が秩父線だからって馬鹿にしたろ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.34,0:10:54.60,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,あ　やめて
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.11,0:10:56.92,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,おい　こらー
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.92,0:10:59.64,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶に何してんだあ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.64,0:11:02.17,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,けど今日はじょーっと遅いのです
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.47,0:11:05.82,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,帰ってきたらめっしなきゃ　べんすかべえ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.82,0:11:06.43,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.43,0:11:07.37,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,よし
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.37,0:11:09.57,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,じゃあ私も一緒にメエしちゃお
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.94,0:11:11.60,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,そうしてください
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.37,0:11:44.69,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,マコト先生
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.44,0:11:46.89,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,山田　これは
Dialogue: 1,0:11:46.89,0:11:47.84,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,話は後
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.84,0:11:48.90,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,助けるから来て
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.15,0:12:02.14,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,貴様だ　俺様の基地で何をしている
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.14,0:12:02.77,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,でっか
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.77,0:12:03.92,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,てゆか普通
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.92,0:12:05.17,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,そういうことね
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.17,0:12:06.14,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,どうやって逃げた
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.14,0:12:07.46,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,教えないよバーカ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.46,0:12:09.29,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,これ以上勝手な真似をしてみろ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.29,0:12:11.96,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,その首根っこ引き抜いて　ギッタンギッタンにして
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.96,0:12:13.81,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,勝手にやってんのはあんたでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.81,0:12:14.77,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,全部聞いた
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.77,0:12:16.46,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,ちょ　近いだろ　なんだお前
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.46,0:12:19.21,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,なんでみんな従ってんだろって思ってたけど
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.21,0:12:20.72,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,体大きいだけじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.07,0:12:22.85,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,知ったほら口を利くな
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.85,0:12:25.42,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,俺様はアホのくせに生きがるギャルが大っ嫌いなんて
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.42,0:12:27.68,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,私もあんたみたいなの超嫌いだし
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.68,0:12:28.80,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,いや　お前
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.80,0:12:30.87,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,俺の方がもっともっともっと嫌いだ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.87,0:12:32.21,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,ちょ　おい　何してる
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.21,0:12:33.56,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,さっさと撃て
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.56,0:12:34.43,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,てぇ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.76,0:12:36.07,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,撃てぇ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.07,0:12:38.26,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,こんなの痛がゆいだけだ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.26,0:12:39.47,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,おりゃ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.47,0:12:41.36,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,わすいミサイル発射
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.32,0:12:43.17,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,おりゃ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.61,0:12:44.99,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,二度はきかないやん
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.99,0:12:46.83,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,わー　分かったぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.83,0:12:49.61,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,貴様らドクターを解除してここを乗っ取るつもりだな
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.61,0:12:50.29,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,は
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.29,0:12:52.42,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,そんなことは絶対にさせんぞ　アホギャル
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.42,0:12:53.95,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あんたバッカじゃないの
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.95,0:12:54.44,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,へい
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.50,0:13:00.01,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留ちゃん　ナイス
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.01,0:13:00.99,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ここは任せて
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.99,0:13:01.82,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,晶届行って
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.82,0:13:02.20,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,えん
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.20,0:13:02.94,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,早く
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.94,0:13:04.08,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,ぼーっとしてんな
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.08,0:13:05.72,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,さっさとドクターを撃て
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.72,0:13:07.30,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,撃て撃て撃て撃てー
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.21,0:13:09.61,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,おりゃー
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.58,0:13:12.60,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,逃がすな
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.60,0:13:14.36,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,撃て撃て撃てー
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.45,0:13:26.40,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ただいま
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.40,0:13:27.21,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲実ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.21,0:13:28.85,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,おざい
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.85,0:13:30.38,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,アクション・フィガーあ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.38,0:13:31.29,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,え　何
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.29,0:13:33.10,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ドクターと稲荷山公園の人
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.10,0:13:35.11,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶直したらすぐ静留ちゃん助けに行く
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.11,0:13:36.77,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留ってどういうこと
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.77,0:13:37.62,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ほら晶
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.62,0:13:38.75,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,お医者さん来たから
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.75,0:13:40.83,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,待って　私は医者じゃないぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.83,0:13:41.30,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,はあ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.30,0:13:42.68,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,だってドクターでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.68,0:13:44.20,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,私は科学者だ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.80,0:13:47.24,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,じゃあ全然駄目じゃん　直せないじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.24,0:13:49.02,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,とりあえず話を聞かせてみろ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.02,0:13:51.42,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,意味ないってお医者じゃなきゃ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.42,0:13:54.58,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,少し前　お尻に生えてた茸を抜いたら
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.58,0:13:55.93,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,別人になっちゃって
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.93,0:13:58.27,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,体もどんどん動かなくなってて
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.62,0:13:59.37,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,見るぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.04,0:14:03.60,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,晶君と言ったか
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.60,0:14:06.92,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,茸が抜けてから体が重い以外で何か変化は
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.92,0:14:09.19,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,うん　とんねー
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.19,0:14:11.75,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,頭ん中がすうすうする
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.75,0:14:13.29,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,君たちは運がいい
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.29,0:14:15.45,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,7Gが原因なら医者には直せん
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.45,0:14:17.27,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,先生なら直せるの
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.27,0:14:18.11,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,急ぐな
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.11,0:14:20.06,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,科学者といえど分野が違う
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.06,0:14:23.67,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,だが7Gの研究に携わっていた分推測はできる
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.67,0:14:24.09,JP-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.09,0:14:25.71,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,先生が7Gの
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.71,0:14:28.02,JP-Main-Down,Man,0,0,0,,じゃあボスがドクターを押されていたのは
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.02,0:14:32.32,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,私の経歴を知り　街を元に戻されると思ったようだ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.81,0:14:34.89,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,我々は今回おきたことを
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.89,0:14:37.27,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,7G「ウェーブ・ブレーン」現象と呼んでいる
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.27,0:14:38.97,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,セブン・イレブン　なに
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.97,0:14:40.77,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,7Gの影響下では
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.77,0:14:44.46,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,人の体もその意識のありようで大きく変化し得るんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.46,0:14:45.97,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,それを元に戻せば
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.97,0:14:47.15,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,もっと分かるように
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.15,0:14:49.30,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,つまり　晶君の変化は
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.30,0:14:53.20,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,茸と共に大切なものを取られたという意識によるもの
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.20,0:14:55.59,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,ならばそれが戻ったと思い込むよう
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.59,0:14:57.05,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,茸を食わせればいい
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.05,0:14:57.81,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,えっ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.81,0:14:59.90,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,茸だ　持ってないか
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.90,0:15:01.03,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,ありません
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.03,0:15:02.81,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,また東吾野行くの
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.81,0:15:05.62,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,いや　確かボスの部屋に生えていたな
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.62,0:15:06.25,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,茸が
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.55,0:15:08.34,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,善治郎が生きていたら
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.34,0:15:10.63,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,もう少しマシな手段が取れたかもしれんが
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.63,0:15:12.38,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,え　善治郎って
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.38,0:15:15.23,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,吾野の　平善治郎さんですか
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.23,0:15:16.59,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,お前たちなぜ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.59,0:15:18.08,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,奴は生きているのか
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.08,0:15:20.47,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,生きてます　けどボケてます
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.86,0:15:23.20,JP-Main-Down,Nadeko,0,0,0,,善治郎
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.95,0:15:31.78,JP-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,うにゃうにゃ　ゴー
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.78,0:15:34.15,JP-Main-Down,Surgeon,0,0,0,,うにゃうにゃ手術　開始します
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.71,0:15:42.60,JP-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,逃げろ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.41,0:15:45.39,JP-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,立ち止まるな　急げ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.39,0:15:46.82,JP-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,早く行け
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.90,0:15:53.47,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,善治郎は私の恩人だ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.89,0:15:56.42,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,とにかく今は晶君だ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.68,0:16:05.48,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ここって　どこ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.79,0:16:07.22,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,俺様の部屋だ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.58,0:16:09.06,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,どうする気
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.06,0:16:10.85,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,死刑にして骨にして飾る
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.68,0:16:13.29,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,そうだな それもいい
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.29,0:16:16.40,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,動ける時点で負ける気しないけどね
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.40,0:16:18.10,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,はい　ですね
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.17,0:16:20.75,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なんでこんなことしてんの
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.32,0:16:23.54,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,単なる弱い者いじめじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.54,0:16:27.45,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,基地が　好きだったんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.45,0:16:28.29,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.29,0:16:29.39,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,格好いいだろ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.39,0:16:32.60,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,戦闘機とか　ヘリとか　いろんな車があって
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.03,0:16:36.01,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,ずっと憧れてたけど誰にも言わなかった
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.01,0:16:38.91,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,でも初めて何人か友達ができてさ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.91,0:16:41.59,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,そいつらに基地で働きたいって話だ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.92,0:16:43.42,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,爆笑されたよ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.42,0:16:46.55,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,お前の頭と運動神経じゃ無理に決まってるだろって
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.29,0:16:52.36,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,そんで7G起こってここに来たら
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.90,0:16:56.20,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,どうせくだらねえとか狂ってるとしか思ってねえんだろ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.15,0:16:58.22,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,ちょ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.22,0:16:59.89,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,なんでそんな顔すんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.89,0:17:01.19,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,うん　別に
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.81,0:17:05.14,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,池袋　行ったことある
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.14,0:17:05.60,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.60,0:17:07.18,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,池袋行くのか
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.18,0:17:08.67,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,あそこ危ねえって
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.67,0:17:11.42,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,そんなヤバいとこより　俺とここにいろよ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.42,0:17:12.42,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,な　なな
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.55,0:17:14.87,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,ちなみに
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.39,0:17:18.84,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,お前がここに残るなら　友達を逃してやって
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.05,0:17:26.68,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留ちゃんと茸渡せ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.68,0:17:29.68,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,だからギャルは嫌いなんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.94,0:17:36.44,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,いい加減に観念しろこんにゃろ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.44,0:17:37.44,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,黙れ黙れ黙れ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.44,0:17:38.29,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,クソでかギャル
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.29,0:17:40.76,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,俺様の基地は絶対渡さん
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.56,0:17:56.33,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.94,0:18:13.08,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,これ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.90,0:18:15.96,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,教科書　御免
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.96,0:18:16.54,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.54,0:18:17.98,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,いよ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.03,0:18:23.59,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,目標に命中
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.59,0:18:24.14,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,おい
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.14,0:18:25.46,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,あのままじゃまずいぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.74,0:18:27.92,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,はいまずいですね
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.92,0:18:29.00,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,あいつが
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.00,0:18:29.59,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.17,0:18:35.72,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,おいおいおいおい
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.72,0:18:36.75,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,お前馬鹿　助けろ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.75,0:18:38.21,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,助けろ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.24,0:19:50.16,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あれ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.66,0:19:51.97,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,やっちゃった
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.25,0:19:54.69,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,やっちゃった
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.56,0:20:04.40,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,まずいのです
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.40,0:20:05.79,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,もう食べません
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.79,0:20:07.06,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,プンプンプン
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.55,0:20:09.77,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,駄目が
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.77,0:20:10.51,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,どうしよう
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.02,0:20:12.89,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,このままじゃ晶ちゃん　
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.40,0:20:16.70,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,こんな晶じゃない
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.56,0:20:21.77,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ひねくれてて　小難しいこんな本ばっか読んでなきゃ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.12,0:20:24.11,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,あの本はなんだけ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.35,0:20:27.92,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あんたの　大好物でしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.44,0:20:32.09,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,8,,{\an8}晶
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.82,0:20:30.25,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,大好物
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.58,0:20:31.71,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,え　ちょちょちょっと
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.71,0:20:32.65,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲実ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.08,0:20:32.65,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,8,,{\an8}待て
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.65,0:20:33.34,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.34,0:20:34.78,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,うまくいくかもしれん
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.78,0:20:37.76,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あの時のお返しだ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.48,0:20:42.55,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,何すんだ馬鹿玲実
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.55,0:20:43.69,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,死ぬじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.69,0:20:45.05,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,サディストがあんたは
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.05,0:20:45.49,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,サデ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.49,0:20:46.46,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,サディズム
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.46,0:20:47.88,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,すなわち加虐性欲
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.88,0:20:49.60,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,他人に身体的な虐待や
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.60,0:20:51.31,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,全身的な苦痛を与えることで
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.31,0:20:53.08,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,性的興奮を得ること
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.08,0:20:54.96,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,わかんなきゃマルキ・ド・サド読め
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.96,0:20:57.70,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,まあ馬鹿には珍紛漢紛だろうけどね
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.70,0:20:59.56,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.02,0:21:01.17,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.17,0:21:02.85,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,私の龍彦
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.85,0:21:05.20,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,これもあと一冊しかないんだぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.20,0:21:07.71,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,しかもそれ保存用がら読めないんだぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.71,0:21:09.28,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.28,0:21:10.66,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,離れる
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.89,0:21:15.76,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,8,,{\an8}下ろせ　下ろせよ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.18,0:21:14.50,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あれどこ行くの
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.50,0:21:18.24,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,7Gで馬鹿でかくなったさやまこに無人島ができてな
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.24,0:21:20.34,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,8,,{\an8}下ろせ来て
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.57,0:21:20.33,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,あそこならそうそう出られない
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.34,0:21:24.22,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,あんな何もねえとこやだ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.22,0:21:26.65,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,私は善治郎のもとへ向かう
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.65,0:21:29.42,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,この状況を良くする方法が見つかるかもしれん
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.68,0:21:30.99,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,でもここは
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.99,0:21:33.69,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,私たちで自警団を作ることになりました
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.69,0:21:36.30,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ああそっか　武器あるし
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.30,0:21:38.55,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ドクター私らと逆向きの旅だね
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.55,0:21:40.07,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,このサイズだ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.07,0:21:43.15,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,車にありったけの燃料を積んでも何日かかるか
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.41,0:21:46.04,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,気をつけて　何あるかわかんないし
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.04,0:21:47.37,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,それは私らもだけど
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.37,0:21:50.50,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,目的地への道のりとはそういうものだ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.50,0:21:51.74,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,だからこそ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.74,0:21:54.08,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,一歩を踏み出す勇気には価値がある
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.69,0:22:04.14,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,ブレースレット　また作ったけ
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.14,0:22:05.37,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,本当
