Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.29,0:00:02.91,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,學習到底是為了什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.91,0:00:04.32,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,一點也不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.32,0:00:07.69,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,不懂的話 或許是為了弄明白吧
