Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.56,0:00:21.65,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,靜留你許了什麼願望呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.65,0:00:22.70,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.70,0:00:23.72,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你許了什麼願呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.72,0:00:24.36,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:25.24,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.03,0:00:35.07,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,上啊 撫子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.07,0:00:37.35,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,打倒對方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.52,0:00:41.39,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,去啊 戰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:42.29,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,加油
