Comment: 0,0:02:18.87,0:02:20.87,ZH-Main-Down,,0,0,0,,正文
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:22.48,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這什麼鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.48,0:02:24.09,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,靜留你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.09,0:02:27.73,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這肯定是剛才那群小人搞的鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.73,0:02:28.83,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:30.62,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,完全掙不開
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:31.83,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,靜留呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.00,0:02:36.91,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.91,0:02:39.97,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,話說他們發射了很多東西 比如導彈什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:42.27,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不是什麼點 是導彈 是導彈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:44.06,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,除此之外 還有迷你士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:45.97,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,砰砰朝我們開槍 痛不欲生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:47.16,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,肯定就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.16,0:02:49.74,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,但因為質量很小 所以威力也不大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.74,0:02:50.55,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.55,0:02:51.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不知道 大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.68,0:02:54.07,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,比起這個 繩子呀怎麼解開
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.28,0:02:54.81,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,{\an8}對 確實
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.81,0:02:57.61,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.05,0:03:15.01,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,你們倆 到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.30,0:03:16.89,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,首先 把我們放開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.89,0:03:17.70,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,回答我們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.70,0:03:19.08,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不要 放開我再說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:22.59,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,那麼 到你死之前都可以保持沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:25.74,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我們從吾野來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.57,0:03:27.82,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.38,0:03:30.84,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,吾野的人 也沒有任何變化嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:32.91,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,也 再說一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.91,0:03:35.84,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,我是問 吾野的大家是否還和以前一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:39.18,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我們雖然沒有 但遲早會變成動物的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.45,0:03:40.99,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,你們來這裡 做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:43.68,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,散步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.15,0:03:44.77,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\an8}我們在找醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:45.99,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,為什麼說出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:47.10,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,難道不說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.10,0:03:48.88,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,本來想一點點說的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:50.47,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你這樣我又不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.47,0:03:52.82,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,全部都說出來 討價還價的份都沒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:55.00,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸 讓他們放開後再說話 我不是說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:56.92,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你這樣子大叔一點變通的餘地都沒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:59.40,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,最開始 你那種態度就不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:01.02,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,可是大叔我好不爽他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.02,0:04:03.43,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我也好不爽啊 這臭男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:05.37,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,轉起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.19,0:04:12.35,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什麼什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:14.02,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,等等等會 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:15.62,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,快點停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:17.23,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,{\an8}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:17.23,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,臉也好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:17.99,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,停止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:21.90,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,好吵啊 你們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:23.88,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,現在是我在質問你們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:25.44,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,別自顧自就拌起嘴來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.44,0:04:27.29,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,你倆吵架 卻說我壞話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.29,0:04:28.49,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,突然非常火大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:29.49,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,我才沒火大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:31.13,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,誰會跟一個小女孩發脾氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.13,0:04:32.32,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,我可是隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.32,0:04:34.03,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,為什麼隊長要對一個小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.03,0:04:34.50,ZH-Main-Down,Soldier,0,0,0,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:35.94,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:39.30,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,你們說你們要找醫生 吾野應該也有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:41.54,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我們在找刀客塔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.33,0:04:44.82,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,為什麼找刀客塔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:46.22,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我的朋友長了蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:48.66,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,雖然拔下來了 但是很可能快要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.66,0:04:49.73,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:51.62,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,那也是7G影響造成的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:53.06,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那當然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:54.95,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,肯定是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:55.68,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,絕對是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:04:58.39,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,果然 老闆說的是對的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:00.41,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什麼情況 剛剛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.41,0:05:01.76,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,我們立刻向上級匯報
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:02.54,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,等會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.54,0:05:04.22,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,話都說完了放我們下來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:06.02,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,我並未做出過這樣的承諾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.02,0:05:08.92,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,我們不能向外部來者洩露城市的資訊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:09.81,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:12.57,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,這是我們「英明」的老闆做的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:13.04,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:16.68,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,奉老闆之命 明天 你們的骨架
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:19.79,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,將會在狹山市立博物館的曙光劍齒象骨架旁展出
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.05,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,骨架是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.86,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,變成骨架的話說明已經死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:24.32,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,是死刑啊 這
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.83,0:05:26.35,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,等會 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.35,0:05:29.56,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,放開我 你這豌豆大小的垃圾蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:31.65,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,電流正常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.65,0:05:32.77,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,電壓正常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.09,0:05:33.35,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,{\an8}撫子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:35.88,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,安東尼 快點過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:37.92,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,好 稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:40.31,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,波奇 小晶她叫我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:42.64,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,快點過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.51,0:05:43.28,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\an8}好好好行行行 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:45.41,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,小晶 怎麼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.41,0:05:48.76,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,玲實和靜留 她們倆去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:51.48,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,小晶一個人好孤獨好無聊噗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.48,0:05:52.53,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:55.09,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,她們肯定很快就回來的 再稍微等等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.09,0:05:58.59,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,她們兩人絕對會繞行 去偷吃米飯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.59,0:06:01.50,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,所以我也要和安東尼一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:05.33,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,波奇 檢查結束前就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.04,0:06:09.42,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,安東尼 毛茸茸的好可愛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.42,0:06:12.68,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你的臉越來越變得可愛了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:15.31,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊敲 手好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:17.04,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,別這樣 會出血的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.04,0:06:18.87,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,現在不是說這個的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:20.06,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,手鍊可是會斷掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:23.05,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,聽聽我的想法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:23.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.68,0:06:26.37,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,已經知道這個城鎮裡確實有個很好的醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:27.08,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.08,0:06:29.02,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,還有就是要找到對方 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.02,0:06:29.82,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:31.54,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,解開這個的方法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.54,0:06:32.33,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這個還沒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:33.03,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那這
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:34.55,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這件事才是最重要的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.55,0:06:36.66,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,期望越高 失望越大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:39.08,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,真的是 難道就沒好辦法了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.61,0:06:42.29,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,等會等會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:44.16,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,等一下 大姐姐等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:46.54,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,拜託你幫我們鬆綁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.54,0:06:49.43,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我們並沒有傷害你的意圖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:52.68,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我們只是想找刀客塔 讓其幫助我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.41,0:06:55.14,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,要是和你們說話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:57.84,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,老闆會把我剝成骨架 然後展出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:06:59.58,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,所以那個老闆是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.58,0:07:01.59,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,回答的話也會被做成骨架
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.59,0:07:03.77,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那你根本不用靠近過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:05.53,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,難道你有理由必須這麼做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.53,0:07:09.75,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,我是這裡的清潔工 負責清掃垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.75,0:07:12.15,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,要是不乾淨 也會被製成骨辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.15,0:07:12.98,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那那
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:14.88,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我們也和你一起撿垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:15.92,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,等會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.92,0:07:16.95,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,尿尿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.82,0:07:19.04,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:20.74,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我想放水 就在這
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:22.77,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,剛剛就想要去上廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:25.31,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,現在我忍不住了 要在這噓噓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:28.70,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,把公園搞髒也是沒辦法的事情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.70,0:07:30.38,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我也想要屙尿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:31.63,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,會把一切搞亂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:32.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,咱可不管呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:35.20,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,如果你給我們鬆綁 我們絕對會搞定老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:38.06,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,靜留的吾野柔術可是真的不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:39.94,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我也是了不得的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.94,0:07:42.67,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,要嘛幫我 要嘛骨辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:44.69,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,或者被尿一身 然後被做成骨架
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:45.87,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你選
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:48.93,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 馬上要出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.71,0:07:50.90,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,謝謝姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:52.09,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,好痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.09,0:07:52.88,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:54.09,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,去幹掉老闆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.09,0:07:55.71,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是先去看看刀客塔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.09,0:07:58.94,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,博士她 被老闆拘留了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.94,0:08:00.45,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸 不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:03.92,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,所以首先 要求助於知曉博士藏身之地的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:05.45,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,都沒人在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.45,0:08:07.53,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,畢竟有外出禁止令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.53,0:08:09.93,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,所以 刀客塔為什麼被拘留呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:12.35,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,這要從頭開始講起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:17.17,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,我們大家的變化 聽說高機率是7G事件所造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.17,0:08:21.19,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,城市不斷膨脹 然後突然逆向變得非常小
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:24.39,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,在這其中 有一個居民將我們團結了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.39,0:08:25.61,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,那就是博士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:27.67,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,戈帕·誠·安斯特朗姆女士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:29.35,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好強 無論工作還是名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.35,0:08:31.82,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,大家推舉誠老師為領袖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:35.48,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,除了大小以外 生活水準基本維持不變
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.48,0:08:38.58,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,但是就在這時 老闆出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:41.01,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,老闆很快就支配了這座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:43.41,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,因為是領袖 便抓捕了誠老師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:45.15,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,然後把她監禁在某個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.15,0:08:46.84,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,老闆這麼厲害的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:48.21,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,最後居民們被分為
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:51.00,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,服從老闆的 即上等稻荷山市民
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:54.81,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,自由被剝奪的 下等稻荷山市民
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.81,0:08:58.43,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,我們是下等稻荷山市民 全部都在管理之中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:00.94,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,完全是為了依靠基礎設施而生存的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.94,0:09:02.87,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,基建是孑孓的伙伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:04.71,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,這座城市中基地的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:07.41,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,都是為了滿足老闆的癖好而強迫人發電
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.41,0:09:08.76,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這樣太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:10.87,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,大家都放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.87,0:09:13.52,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,但是 要是誠老師能夠回來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.52,0:09:15.91,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,或許能再一次 挺直腰板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.91,0:09:17.82,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,因此我們才在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:18.36,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.74,0:09:25.58,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,靜留 怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:44.72,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.72,0:09:47.05,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,請告訴我們誠老師所在的位置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.05,0:09:49.35,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,作為曾經的上等市民 你們應該知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:52.07,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:55.06,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,情報源絕對不要暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.06,0:09:56.18,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.18,0:09:58.09,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,現在在稻荷山公園
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:10:00.02,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,正在尋找醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.02,0:10:02.08,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,為什麼要去找醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:02.71,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,生病了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.71,0:10:03.42,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.42,0:10:05.93,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不是已經說過 小晶身上長了蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:07.19,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,我知道蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:08.20,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,醫生什麼的我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:10.95,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,稻荷山這應該有個醫生在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.95,0:10:11.91,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.91,0:10:14.85,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,不是的 吧吧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.22,0:10:17.45,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,撫子姐是不是有困難了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:18.82,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我的臉寫滿了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:21.76,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,實際上 小晶我也是問題少女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:24.68,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,身體逐漸扭曲變形動彈不得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:24.68,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\an8}小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:26.83,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但是不用擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.83,0:10:30.99,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,咱要是有困難 無論何時玲實她都會來幫我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:34.18,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這可是讓我肚子疼了好久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.18,0:10:36.23,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我沒想到你真的會去「吃書」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.23,0:10:38.55,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,教科書已經用不了了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:39.59,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,{\an8}是你把它撕爛吃掉的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.59,0:10:41.09,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我要和你絕交
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.09,0:10:42.19,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,哼 我不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:44.54,ZH-Main-Down,Boy A,0,0,0,,喂 你看什麼書
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:46.55,ZH-Main-Down,Boy B,0,0,0,,敲 好無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:47.62,ZH-Main-Down,Boy B,0,0,0,,全都是漢字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:49.24,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我覺得很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.24,0:10:50.01,ZH-Main-Down,Boy C,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.01,0:10:53.34,ZH-Main-Down,Boy C,0,0,0,,你就想取笑西吾野在秩父線上而不在西武池袋線上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:54.60,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,啊 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.11,0:10:56.92,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,喂 你這群傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:10:59.64,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,對小晶做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:02.17,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但是今天稍微晚了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:05.82,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,回來之後要好好說她 笨得跟豬一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:06.43,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:07.37,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:09.57,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那我也一起說教說教她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:11.60,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,請務必這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.37,0:11:44.69,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,誠老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.44,0:11:46.89,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,山田 她們是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:47.84,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,之後再聊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.84,0:11:48.90,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我們來幫助你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:12:02.14,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,你們這群人 在我的基地裡想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:02.77,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.77,0:12:03.92,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不如說挺普通的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.92,0:12:05.17,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,確實如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.17,0:12:06.14,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,你們怎麼跑掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:07.46,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,才不告訴你 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.46,0:12:09.29,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,你再擅自模仿他們試試
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:11.96,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,我會把你頭拔掉 弄得你亂七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:13.81,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,自作主張的人是你才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.81,0:12:14.77,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我全都聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.77,0:12:16.46,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,等 好近 你想做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:19.21,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我原本想為什麼大家要遵從你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:20.72,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,原來只是體型較大而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:22.85,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,既然知道就別說出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:25.42,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,老子最討厭的就是蠢蠢活著的辣妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.42,0:12:27.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,老娘也是超級討厭像你這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:28.80,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,不是 你這
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.80,0:12:30.87,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,我比你更加更加更加討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.87,0:12:32.21,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,你 快 摸什麼魚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:33.56,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,快點攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:34.43,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.76,0:12:36.07,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.07,0:12:38.26,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這點傷痛算不了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.26,0:12:39.47,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.47,0:12:41.36,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,核水導彈發射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:43.17,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,咪西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:44.99,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,才不會上兩次當
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:46.83,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,好 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.83,0:12:49.61,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,你們是想赦免博士 然後占領這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:50.29,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:52.42,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,我絕對不會讓你得逞的 笨蛋辣妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.42,0:12:53.95,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你難道是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.95,0:12:54.44,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:13:00.01,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,靜留 好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.01,0:13:00.99,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這裡交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.99,0:13:01.82,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你先去小晶那
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:02.20,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.20,0:13:02.94,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.94,0:13:04.08,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,發什麼呆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.08,0:13:05.72,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,快點向博士攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:07.30,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,攻擊多次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.21,0:13:09.61,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:12.60,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,別讓她跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:14.36,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,攻擊攻擊攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:26.40,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:27.21,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲實
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.21,0:13:28.85,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:30.38,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,動作小玩偶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.38,0:13:31.29,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,欸 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:33.10,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,她們是稻荷山公園的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.10,0:13:35.11,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,等救治好小晶 我馬上去幫靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:36.77,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留她 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:37.62,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,快看小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:38.75,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,醫生來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:40.83,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,等會 我不是醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.83,0:13:41.30,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:42.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你不是刀客塔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:44.20,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,我是科學家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:47.24,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那完全沒用啊 你治不好她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:49.02,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,總而言之先告訴我發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.02,0:13:51.42,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,有什麼意義啊 你又不是醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:54.58,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,之前 她的屁股上長了蘑菇 拔掉之後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:55.93,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,就好像變成其他人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:58.27,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,身體越來越無法動彈了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:13:59.37,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:03.60,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,晶小姐你描述一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:06.92,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,蘑菇拔出後身體除了變得沉重以外有沒其它的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.92,0:14:09.19,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,嗯 我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.19,0:14:11.75,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,腦袋裡像是有風呼呼吹過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:13.29,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,你們真的非常幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:15.45,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,如果是7G的原因 醫生根本治不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:17.27,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,老師您能治好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.27,0:14:18.11,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,別急
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:20.06,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,就算是科學家 研究的領域也有區分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:23.67,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,但是我參與了7G的研究 大概能推測出一二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:24.09,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:25.71,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,老師您參與了7G
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:28.02,ZH-Main-Down,Man,0,0,0,,那麼老闆推翻博士您…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.02,0:14:32.32,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,他們知道我的經歷 我以為這能夠讓城市恢復如初
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:34.89,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,我們認為當前所發生的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:37.27,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,是被稱為「7G腦波干涉」的現象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:38.97,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,7-11 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.97,0:14:40.77,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,在7G的影響下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:44.46,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,人類的身體也會隨著意識的認知發生變化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.46,0:14:45.97,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,要是想要恢復如初
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.97,0:14:47.15,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,說得更加明白點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:49.30,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,也就是說 晶小姐的變化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.30,0:14:53.20,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,是因為意識到自己某些重要的東西和蘑菇一起被帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:55.59,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,那麼如果把「思想」給加回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.59,0:14:57.05,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,吃點蘑菇或許會好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.05,0:14:57.81,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:14:59.90,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,蘑菇 你們沒帶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.90,0:15:01.03,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.03,0:15:02.81,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,還要去東吾野嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:05.62,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,不用 我記得老闆的屋裡長的有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:06.25,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,蘑菇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:08.34,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,如果善治郎還活著的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:10.63,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,或許我們能夠採取更好的應對方法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:12.38,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸 善治郎的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:15.23,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是吾野的 平善治郎先生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.23,0:15:16.59,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,你們為什麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.59,0:15:18.08,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,那傢伙還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:20.47,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,還活著 但是變成搞笑擔當了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.86,0:15:23.20,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeko,0,0,0,,善治郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:31.78,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,軟綿綿 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:34.15,ZH-Main-Down,Surgeon,0,0,0,,軟綿綿手術 準備開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:42.60,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.41,0:15:45.39,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,別站這裡 繼續走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.39,0:15:46.82,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,快點走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:53.47,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,善治郎是我的恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:56.42,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,總而言之現在最重要是晶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:05.48,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這裡是 哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:07.22,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,俺的房間呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.58,0:16:09.06,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你打算幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.06,0:16:10.85,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,判我死刑拿我骨頭去裝飾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.68,0:16:13.29,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,確實 這也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:16.40,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我還能動的時候 可是不會覺得自己輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.40,0:16:18.10,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,對 確實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:20.75,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,為什麼要做這些事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:23.54,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你這樣只是恃強凌弱罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:27.45,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,基地 我喜歡這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:28.29,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.29,0:16:29.39,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,很帥是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.39,0:16:32.60,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,戰鬥機 直升機 還有各式各樣的車
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:36.01,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,我雖然一直都很憧憬 但從未和別人提起過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:38.91,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,但我最初的時候也交到了一些朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.91,0:16:41.59,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,我說也想和他們一樣在基地裡工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.92,0:16:43.42,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,然後就被笑爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.42,0:16:46.55,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,他們說 以你的頭腦和運動神經當然是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.29,0:16:52.36,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,然後7G發生後 就來到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:56.20,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,反正那群人只會認為你無聊至極瘋狂愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.15,0:16:58.22,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.22,0:16:59.89,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,為什麼你看起來這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:01.19,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,唔 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:05.14,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,池袋 你有去過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:05.60,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:07.18,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,你要去池袋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:08.67,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,那裡很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:11.42,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,比起在那個鬼地方 和我在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:12.42,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,行 行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:14.87,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,順帶一提
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.39,0:17:18.84,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,如果你能留在這裡 就放你的朋友走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.05,0:17:26.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,靜留和蘑菇交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.68,0:17:29.68,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,都說了我最討厭辣妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:36.44,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,是時候放棄你的想法吧 矮窮挫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.44,0:17:37.44,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,閉嘴閉嘴閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.44,0:17:38.29,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,可惡的辣妹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.29,0:17:40.76,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,俺的基地絕對不會讓給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.56,0:17:56.33,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:13.08,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:15.96,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,教科書 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:16.54,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.54,0:18:17.98,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:23.59,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,目標命中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.59,0:18:24.14,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:25.46,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,那樣子的話可糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.74,0:18:27.92,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,確實 糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:29.00,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:29.59,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:35.72,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,等等等等會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:36.75,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,你們這群笨蛋 快點幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.75,0:18:38.21,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,快點幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.24,0:19:50.16,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:51.97,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:54.69,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.56,0:20:04.40,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,這很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:05.79,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,已經吃不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.79,0:20:07.06,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,笨笨笨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.55,0:20:09.77,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:10.51,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:12.89,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,這樣下去的話小晶她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:16.70,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這根本 不是小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:21.77,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,憤世嫉俗 晦澀難懂的這些傻瓜書籍沒有被讀過的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.12,0:20:24.11,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,那本書是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:27.92,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這是你的 最喜歡東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:32.09,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\an8}小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:30.25,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,最喜歡的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:31.71,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸 等等等會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:32.65,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲實
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.08,0:20:32.65,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,{\an8}別動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.65,0:20:33.34,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:34.78,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,或許這樣會有效
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.78,0:20:37.76,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那個時候咱原紙奉還
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:42.55,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你幹什麼鬼笨蛋玲實
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:43.69,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,要死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.69,0:20:45.05,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你是虐待狂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:45.49,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,虐待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.49,0:20:46.46,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,薩德主義
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.46,0:20:47.88,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,說白了就是性虐待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.88,0:20:49.60,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,對他人的身體施加虐待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:51.31,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,在對對方全身造成痛苦的過程中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:53.08,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,享受性興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:54.96,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你不懂就去讀薩德侯爵的書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:57.70,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但這對笨蛋來說根本看不懂罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.70,0:20:59.56,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.02,0:21:01.17,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.17,0:21:02.85,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我的龍彥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.85,0:21:05.20,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,這種書我只剩下一冊了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:07.71,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,而且我還是保存用根本沒讀過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.71,0:21:09.28,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:10.66,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,快離開我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.89,0:21:15.76,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,{\an8}放我下來 放我下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.18,0:21:14.50,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,他要被去哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.50,0:21:18.24,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,7G意外地把狹山湖變大成了個無人島
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.24,0:21:20.34,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,{\an8}快點放我下來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.57,0:21:20.33,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,那個地方幾乎走不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:24.22,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,我不想去鳥不拉屎的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:26.65,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,我會去找善治郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.65,0:21:29.42,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,或許能夠找到方法來改善當前的狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:30.99,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.99,0:21:33.69,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,我們將成立自己的義務警備基層組織
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:36.30,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊確實 畢竟有武器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.30,0:21:38.55,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,博士和我們正好逆向而行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.55,0:21:40.07,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,這個尺寸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:43.15,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,就算盡可能多地給車加滿油不知道需要幾天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.41,0:21:46.04,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,要小心點 發生什麼也不得所知
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.04,0:21:47.37,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這點我們也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.37,0:21:50.50,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,通往目的地的旅程就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.50,0:21:51.74,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.74,0:21:54.08,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,邁出第一步的勇氣是有價值的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.69,0:22:04.14,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,手鍊 我會再做個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.14,0:22:05.37,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,真的嗎
